[I] A BitTorrent program

[T] KTorrent is a BitTorrent application by KDE which allows you to download
[T] files using the BitTorrent protocol. It enables you to run multiple
[T] torrents at the same time and comes with extended features to make it a
[T] full-featured client for BitTorrent.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/ktorrent/

